AJW Portal Display Accounts Dashboard,on this page System Display Header which Contain Language translator Icon and loged in user profile,notification icon,search bar,X sign," + "On Sidebar display Account office all working acion button

AJW Portal's Home Page Display Some AJW Agro Industry Close View,On Page Top Display Language Translator,Login and Register Icon," + "Display C.E.O , G.M and D.G.M Short Profile,on Right Side System Display Notic Board Pannel of AJW Agro Industry
Here we are not allow AJW Portal's user registration,just use login button for login into AJW Portal and go on Accounts Dashbpoard

Notic Board,On Home Page You can see all Notices about AJW Agro Industry
On AJW Portal's Home Page,you can chage the language English/Urdu and AJW Portal display page in set language
Sidebar-Account Support Guide-contain 2 option : Accounts Law Book>>contain all laws about account office,Accounts user Guide>>contain all AJW Portal'function's guide(How to use AJW Portal???)
Sidebar-Accounts General Ledger Reports >>> System display General ledger List Page(Daily/Monthly/Yearly),here create daily/monthly/yearly general ledger report and save in list

Sidebar-Accounts Industry supplier Ledger Reports >>> System display Industry supplier ledger List Page(Daily/Monthly/Yearly),here create daily/monthly/yearly Industry supplier ledger report and save in list

Sidebar-Accounts Internal Account Ledger Reports >>> System display Internal Account ledger List Page(Daily/Monthly/Yearly),here create daily/monthly/yearly Internal Account ledger report and save in list
Sidebar-Accounts Ledger Reports >>> this option contain 4 option :1st General Ledger, 2nd Internal Account Ledger, 3rd Industry Supplier Ledger, 4th Main Bank Account Ledger

Sidebar-Accounts Main Bank Account Ledger Reports >>> System display Main Bank Account ledger List Page(Daily/Monthly/Yearly),here create daily/monthly/yearly Main Bank Account ledger report and save in list
Sidebar-Accounts Monthly/Yearly Reports >>> click on accounts monthly/yearly report,system display Accounts Monthly/Yearly Reports List,here accounts manager create reports and save in list page

Sidebar-Accounts Pdf Reports >>> after all reports varification by D.G.M/G.M then check it with signatures and remarks,if ok then download all Daily sheets,if not ok then clear all error and then send to D.G.M/G.M office

Sidebar-Accounts Pdf Reports >>> Click on accounts pdf reports,system display accounts all reports pdf list table and click on create button,system display pdf file upload form,here accounts manager set file title and select pdf file which contain all daily reports sheets

Sidebar-Accounts Pdf Reports >>> Click on accounts pdf reports,system display accounts all reports pdf list table and click on create button,system display pdf file upload form,here accounts manager set file title and select pdf file which contain all daily reports sheets.

Sidebar-Accounts Repository >>> click on Repository option,system display All accounts report repository list pgae,this folder just use for reports' varification,send to D.G.M/G.M office and D.G.M/G.M send to back accounts office.its varification pannel
Sidebar-Daily Accounts Reports>>> click on Daily Accounts Reports,system display All Daily Accounts Report List Page,here create sheets and save in list page
Sidebar-Dashboard display Key values of account office
